See [TrollDisappearKey test](mdc:tests_source/c1f0fe6f-6907-4f95-820d-47e0a39abe54/c1f0fe6f-6907-4f95-820d-47e0a39abe54.go) for a complete example following this standard.

## Non-Compliance
Tests that do not follow this standard will be inconsistent with the established security testing framework and may interfere with proper artifact cleanup and monitoring.
